{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896193710,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba95d35001gHLUMsJHEFr96B","messageID":"msg_d7ba94f91001HS0Rfi9kfgpFdV","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: id: AR-024\n2: title: DockerService 封装\n3: module: cmd/cli\n4: language: Python\n5: size: M\n6: status: open\n7: \n8: # AR-024: DockerService 封装\n9: # Module: cmd/cli\n10: # Language: Python\n11: # Size: M\n12: \n13: # OpenSpec Metadata\n14: openspec:\n15:   version: \"1.0\"\n16:   project: agentcube\n17: \n18: # Architecture Requirement\n19: requirement:\n20:   type: service-layer\n21:   description: |\n22:     Encapsulate Docker operations into a DockerService class within the cmd/cli module.\n23:     This service will provide a clean, testable abstraction over Docker CLI commands\n24:     and Docker SDK for Python, supporting container lifecycle management, image\n25:     operations, and network/volume management for agent deployment.\n26: \n27: # Scope\n28: scope:\n29:   in:\n30:     - DockerService class implementation\n31:     - Container lifecycle operations (create, start, stop, remove)\n32:     - Image management (pull, build, list, remove)\n33:     - Network operations (create, list, remove)\n34:     - Volume management (create, list, remove)\n35:     - Error handling and retry logic\n36:     - Configuration management for Docker connection\n37:   out:\n38:     - Kubernetes service implementation (AR-023)\n39:     - Container registry backend\n40:     - Multi-node Docker Swarm support\n41:     - Web UI for container management\n42: \n43: # Acceptance Criteria\n44: acceptance:\n45:   - DockerService provides clean API for all Docker operations\n46:   - Supports both Docker CLI fallback and Docker SDK\n47:   - Handles connection errors gracefully\n48:   - Provides detailed error messages\n49:   - Supports async/await pattern for long-running operations\n50:   - Returns structured data for all operations\n51:   - Unit testable with mock interfaces\n52: \n53: # References\n54: references:\n55:   - https://docker-py.readthedocs.io/\n56:   - https://docs.docker.com/engine/api/\n57: \n58: # Estimation\n59: estimation:\n60:   size: M\n61:   story_points: 5\n62:   days: 3\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: AR-024\ntitle: DockerService 封装\nmodule: cmd/cli\nlanguage: Python\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-024: DockerService 封装\n# Module: cmd/cli\n# Language: Python\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: service-layer","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775896193684,"end":1775896193708}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896193711,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba9619f001HBJEELNQoYeRxi","messageID":"msg_d7ba94f91001HS0Rfi9kfgpFdV","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/plan.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/plan.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Implementation Plan\n2: \n3: ## Phase 1: Foundation\n4: - [ ] Create DockerService class structure\n5: - [ ] Define exception hierarchy\n6: - [ ] Implement configuration management\n7: - [ ] Set up backend detection logic\n8: \n9: ## Phase 2: Container Operations\n10: - [ ] Implement container creation\n11: - [ ] Implement container start/stop/restart\n12: - [ ] Implement container removal\n13: - [ ] Implement container inspection\n14: - [ ] Implement container listing\n15: \n16: ## Phase 3: Image Operations\n17: - [ ] Implement image pulling\n18: - [ ] Implement image building\n19: - [ ] Implement image listing\n20: - [ ] Implement image removal\n21: - [ ] Add progress callbacks\n22: \n23: ## Phase 4: Network & Volume\n24: - [ ] Implement network creation\n25: - [ ] Implement network listing/removal\n26: - [ ] Implement volume creation\n27: - [ ] Implement volume listing/removal\n28: \n29: ## Phase 5: Error Handling & Testing\n30: - [ ] Implement retry logic\n31: - [ ] Add comprehensive error handling\n32: - [ ] Write unit tests with mocks\n33: - [ ] Write integration tests\n\n(End of file - total 33 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1: Foundation\n- [ ] Create DockerService class structure\n- [ ] Define exception hierarchy\n- [ ] Implement configuration management\n- [ ] Set up backend detection logic\n\n## Phase 2: Container Operations\n- [ ] Implement container creation\n- [ ] Implement container start/stop/restart\n- [ ] Implement container removal\n- [ ] Implement container inspection\n- [ ] Implement container listing\n\n## Phase 3: Image Operations\n- [ ] Implement image pulling\n- [ ] Implement image building\n- [ ] Implement image listing\n- [ ] Implement image removal","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/plan.md","time":{"start":1775896193688,"end":1775896193710}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896193714,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba96636001A4LzNmLFGTA0AI","messageID":"msg_d7ba94f91001HS0Rfi9kfgpFdV","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Design Document\n2: \n3: ## Architecture\n4: \n5: ### Component Diagram\n6: ```\n7: ┌─────────────────┐\n8: │   CLI Commands  │\n9: │  (deploy, etc)  │\n10: └────────┬────────┘\n11:          │\n12: ┌────────▼────────┐\n13: │  DockerService  │\n14: │ (docker_service)│\n15: └────────┬────────┘\n16:          │\n17:     ┌────┴────┐\n18:     ▼         ▼\n19: ┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n20: │Docker │ │Docker │\n21: │ SDK   │ │ CLI   │\n22: └───┬───┘ └───────┘\n23:     │\n24:     ▼\n25: ┌─────────┐\n26: │ Docker  │\n27: │ Daemon  │\n28: └─────────┘\n29: ```\n30: \n31: ## Key Design Decisions\n32: \n33: ### Dual Backend Strategy\n34: - Primary: Docker SDK for Python (docker-py)\n35: - Fallback: Docker CLI subprocess calls\n36: - Automatic detection of available backend\n37: \n38: ### Connection Management\n39: - Support for local Docker socket (unix:///var/run/docker.sock)\n40: - Support for remote Docker daemon via env variables\n41: - Connection pooling for SDK backend\n42: \n43: ### Error Handling\n44: - Custom exception hierarchy for Docker-specific errors\n45: - Structured error messages with actionable suggestions\n46: - Retry logic for transient failures\n47: \n48: ### Async Support\n49: - Async methods for long-running operations (pull, build)\n50: - Callback-based progress reporting\n51: - Timeout configuration per operation\n52: \n53: ## Data Flow\n54: 1. CLI command calls DockerService method\n55: 2. Service validates parameters\n56: 3. Execute via SDK or CLI backend\n57: 4. Parse and structure response\n58: 5. Return result or raise exception\n\n(End of file - total 58 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Design Document\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│   CLI Commands  │\n│  (deploy, etc)  │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n┌────────▼────────┐\n│  DockerService  │\n│ (docker_service)│\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n    ┌────┴────┐\n    ▼         ▼\n┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n│Docker │ │Docker │","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","time":{"start":1775896193690,"end":1775896193712}}}}
