{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896358381,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7baa0f03001Wt6ZXaA0nOrsf3","messageID":"msg_d7ba9ce290011vj4ownMuaLevc","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/plan.md","content":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1: Foundation\n- [ ] Create MetadataService class structure\n- [ ] Define data model schemas using Pydantic\n- [ ] Implement storage interface abstraction\n- [ ] Set up configuration management\n\n## Phase 2: Core CRUD Operations\n- [ ] Implement metadata creation with validation\n- [ ] Implement metadata retrieval by ID\n- [ ] Implement metadata update with versioning\n- [ ] Implement metadata deletion (soft delete)\n- [ ] Implement metadata listing with pagination\n\n## Phase 3: Schema & Validation\n- [ ] Define agent metadata schema\n- [ ] Implement schema validation logic\n- [ ] Add custom validators for business rules\n- [ ] Handle validation error messages\n\n## Phase 4: Search & Query\n- [ ] Implement basic search by keyword\n- [ ] Add filter support (by type, status, tags)\n- [ ] Implement sorting options\n- [ ] Add pagination for search results\n\n## Phase 5: Import/Export\n- [ ] Implement metadata export to JSON\n- [ ] Implement metadata import from JSON\n- [ ] Add validation during import\n- [ ] Handle import error recovery\n\n## Phase 6: Error Handling & Testing\n- [ ] Define custom exception hierarchy\n- [ ] Implement comprehensive error handling\n- [ ] Write unit tests with mocks\n- [ ] Write integration tests\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/plan.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/plan.md","time":{"start":1775896358351,"end":1775896358380}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896358383,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7baa2fd2001anKCawJ3UeMjOW","messageID":"msg_d7ba9ce290011vj4ownMuaLevc","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","content":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Design Document\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│   CLI Commands  │\n│ (agent, config) │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n┌────────▼────────┐\n│ MetadataService │\n│(metadata_service│\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n    ┌────┴────┐\n    ▼         ▼\n┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n│Schema │ │Storage│\n│Validator│ │Interface\n└───┬───┘ └────┬──┘\n    │          │\n    ▼          ▼\n┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐\n│Pydantic │ │ Storage │\n│Models   │ │ Backend │\n└─────────┘ └─────────┘\n```\n\n## Key Design Decisions\n\n### Data Model Design\n- Use Pydantic models for schema definition and validation\n- Base metadata model with extensible fields\n- Version tracking with timestamps\n- Soft delete support for data recovery\n\n### Storage Abstraction\n- Interface-based storage layer\n- Support for multiple backends (file, database)\n- Async operations for I/O bound tasks\n- Connection pooling where applicable\n\n### Schema Validation\n- JSON Schema compatible validation\n- Custom business rule validators\n- Detailed error messages with field paths\n- Pre-save validation hooks\n\n### Versioning Strategy\n- Incremental version numbers\n- Timestamp tracking for audit\n- Change history preservation\n- Rollback capability\n\n## Data Flow\n1. CLI command calls MetadataService method\n2. Service validates input parameters\n3. Schema validation against Pydantic models\n4. Execute storage operation via interface\n5. Return structured result or raise exception\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","time":{"start":1775896358355,"end":1775896358382}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896358385,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7baa5865001D4LcY9Ne28Gtgz","messageID":"msg_d7ba9ce290011vj4ownMuaLevc","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:17","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","content":"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\n\n> **AR ID:** AR-025\n> **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Stage:** ST-1 (Initialized)\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `MetadataService` class provides a unified, high-level interface for managing agent metadata and data models within the AgentCube CLI. This service abstracts storage operations, provides schema validation, versioning support, and enables agent discovery and configuration management.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.1 — Core Service Structure\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.1.1 | Create `MetadataService` class in `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | File exists with proper structure | 0.5h |\n| 1.1.2 | Define `MetadataStorage` abstract interface | Abstract base class with required methods | 0.5h |\n| 1.1.3 | Implement `__init__()` with storage injection | Storage interface properly initialized | 0.25h |\n| 1.1.4 | Add logging support with verbose mode | Logger configuration working | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Core service structure defined.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.2 — Data Model Definitions\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.2.1 | Define `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model | Model with all required fields | 0.5h |\n| 1.2.2 | Define `MetadataVersion` Pydantic model | Version tracking structure | 0.25h |\n| 1.2.3 | Add field validators for business rules | Custom validators implemented | 0.5h |\n| 1.2.4 | Define schema export functionality | JSON schema generation working | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Data models defined with validation.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.3 — CRUD Operations Implementation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.3.1 | Implement `create_metadata()` with validation | Returns created metadata with ID | 0.5h |\n| 1.3.2 | Implement `get_metadata()` by ID | Returns metadata or raises NotFound | 0.25h |\n| 1.3.3 | Implement `update_metadata()` with versioning | Version incremented on update | 0.5h |\n| 1.3.4 | Implement `delete_metadata()` soft delete | Marked as deleted, not removed | 0.25h |\n| 1.3.5 | Implement `list_metadata()` with pagination | Paginated results returned | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** CRUD operations functional.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.4 — Search & Query Implementation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.4.1 | Implement `search_metadata()` by keyword | Keyword search working | 0.5h |\n| 1.4.2 | Add filter by metadata type | Type filter returns correct results | 0.25h |\n| 1.4.3 | Add filter by status | Status filter working | 0.25h |\n| 1.4.4 | Add filter by tags | Tag-based filtering working | 0.25h |\n| 1.4.5 | Implement sorting options | Sort by created/updated/name | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Search and query functional.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.5 — Import/Export Implementation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.5.1 | Implement `export_metadata()` to JSON | JSON file created correctly | 0.5h |\n| 1.5.2 | Implement `import_metadata()` from JSON | Metadata imported with validation | 0.5h |\n| 1.5.3 | Handle import validation errors | Invalid data rejected with errors | 0.25h |\n| 1.5.4 | Support batch import/export | Multiple metadata handled | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Import/export functional.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.6 — Error Handling & Exceptions\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.6.1 | Define `MetadataError` base exception | Base class implemented | 0.25h |\n| 1.6.2 | Define `MetadataNotFoundError` | Raised when ID not found | 0.25h |\n| 1.6.3 | Define `ValidationError` for schema errors | Schema validation errors | 0.25h |\n| 1.6.4 | Define `StorageError` for backend errors | Storage operation errors | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Exception hierarchy defined.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.7 — Unit Tests — Core Service\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.7.1 | Write `TestMetadataServiceInit` — initialization | Service creates correctly | 0.5h |\n| 1.7.2 | Write `TestMetadataServiceCreate` — create operations | Create with validation tested | 0.5h |\n| 1.7.3 | Write `TestMetadataServiceRead` — read operations | Get by ID tested | 0.5h |\n| 1.7.4 | Write `TestMetadataServiceUpdate` — update with versioning | Version increment tested | 0.5h |\n| 1.7.5 | Write `TestMetadataServiceDelete` — soft delete | Delete marks as deleted | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Core service tests pass with >80% coverage.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.8 — Unit Tests — Search & Validation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.8.1 | Write `TestMetadataSearch` — keyword search | Search returns matches | 0.5h |\n| 1.8.2 | Write `TestMetadataFilters` — filter combinations | Multiple filters working | 0.5h |\n| 1.8.3 | Write `TestSchemaValidation` — valid data | Valid data passes | 0.5h |\n| 1.8.4 | Write `TestSchemaValidation` — invalid data | Invalid data rejected | 0.5h |\n| 1.8.5 | Write `TestImportExport` — roundtrip | Export then import works | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Search and validation tests pass.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.9 — Integration Tests\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.9.1 | Create `tests/integration/test_metadata_service.py` | File with fixtures exists | 0.5h |\n| 1.9.2 | Test full CRUD lifecycle | Create → Read → Update → Delete | 1.0h |\n| 1.9.3 | Test search with real data | Search returns correct results | 0.5h |\n| 1.9.4 | Test import/export with files | File I/O works correctly | 0.5h |\n| 1.9.5 | Test error scenarios | Errors handled gracefully | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Integration tests pass.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.10 — Documentation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.10.1 | Add module docstring to `metadata_service.py` | pydoc shows overview | 0.25h |\n| 1.10.2 | Add class docstring to `MetadataService` | Description and usage | 0.25h |\n| 1.10.3 | Add docstrings to all public methods | Args, returns, raises documented | 0.5h |\n| 1.10.4 | Add type hints to all signatures | mypy passes without errors | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Code is well-documented.\n\n---\n\n## ST-1.11 — Lint & Type Check\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 1.11.1 | Run `ruff check` on service files | No lint errors | 0.25h |\n| 1.11.2 | Run `mypy` on service files | No type errors | 0.25h |\n| 1.11.3 | Fix any ruff issues | All checks pass | 0.5h |\n| 1.11.4 | Fix any mypy issues | All checks pass | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Code passes all checks.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Est. Hours |\n|-------|-------|------------|\n| ST-1.1: Core Service Structure | 4 | 1.5h |\n| ST-1.2: Data Model Definitions | 4 | 1.5h |\n| ST-1.3: CRUD Operations | 5 | 2.0h |\n| ST-1.4: Search & Query | 5 | 1.5h |\n| ST-1.5: Import/Export | 4 | 1.5h |\n| ST-1.6: Error Handling | 4 | 1.0h |\n| ST-1.7: Unit Tests — Core | 5 | 2.5h |\n| ST-1.8: Unit Tests — Search | 5 | 2.5h |\n| ST-1.9: Integration Tests | 5 | 3.0h |\n| ST-1.10: Documentation | 4 | 1.5h |\n| ST-1.11: Lint & Type Check | 4 | 1.5h |\n| **Total** | **49** | **20.0h** |\n\n---\n\n## File Deliverables Checklist\n\n- [ ] `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` — MetadataService implementation\n- [ ] `agentcube/services/storage_interface.py` — Storage interface\n- [ ] `agentcube/models/metadata.py` — Pydantic data models\n- [ ] `agentcube/exceptions/metadata.py` — Custom exceptions\n- [ ] `tests/unit/test_metadata_service.py` — Unit tests\n- [ ] `tests/integration/test_metadata_service.py` — Integration tests\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Install verification\npip install -e \".[dev,test]\"\n\n# Import verification\npython -c \"from agentcube.services import MetadataService\"\n\n# Unit test verification\npytest tests/unit/test_metadata_service.py -v\n\n# Integration tests\npytest tests/integration/test_metadata_service.py -v\n\n# Coverage report\npytest --cov=agentcube.services.metadata_service --cov-report=term-missing\n\n# Lint verification\nruff check agentcube/services/metadata_service.py\nmypy agentcube/services/metadata_service.py\n```\n\n---\n\n## Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] All 49 tasks complete\n- [ ] Package installs successfully (`pip install -e .`)\n- [ ] MetadataService importable from `agentcube.services`\n- [ ] All unit tests pass (>80% coverage)\n- [ ] Integration tests pass\n- [ ] Type checking passes (`mypy`)\n- [ ] Linting passes (`ruff`)\n- [ ] Documentation complete with docstrings\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- `pydantic>=2.0.0` — Data validation (already in pyproject.toml)\n- `pytest>=7.4.0` — Testing framework (already present)\n- `pytest-cov>=4.1.0` — Coverage reporting (already present)\n\n---\n\n*AR-025 — Module: cmd/cli — Language: Python — Size: M*\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775896358359,"end":1775896358384}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896358387,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7bab5e92001tJXMy1EID3NB1r","messageID":"msg_d7ba9ce290011vj4ownMuaLevc","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:18","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tests.md","content":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Test Specification\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Service Initialization Tests\n- `test_initializes_with_storage`: Storage interface injected correctly\n- `test_initializes_with_default_storage`: Default storage created when none provided\n- `test_logger_configuration`: Logger set based on verbose flag\n- `test_raises_on_invalid_storage`: Error when storage doesn't implement interface\n\n### Data Model Tests\n- `test_agent_metadata_valid`: Valid metadata passes validation\n- `test_agent_metadata_invalid_name`: Invalid name raises ValidationError\n- `test_agent_metadata_missing_required`: Missing required fields raises error\n- `test_version_increment`: Version increases on update\n- `test_timestamps_auto_set`: Created/updated timestamps populated\n\n### CRUD Operation Tests\n- `test_create_metadata_returns_with_id`: Created metadata has ID assigned\n- `test_create_metadata_validates_input`: Invalid input raises ValidationError\n- `test_get_metadata_by_id`: Retrieval by ID returns correct metadata\n- `test_get_metadata_not_found_raises`: Missing ID raises NotFoundError\n- `test_update_metadata_increments_version`: Version incremented on update\n- `test_update_metadata_updates_timestamp`: Updated timestamp refreshed\n- `test_delete_metadata_soft_delete`: Marked deleted, not removed\n- `test_delete_metadata_not_found_raises`: Missing ID raises NotFoundError\n- `test_list_metadata_returns_paginated`: Paginated results returned\n- `test_list_metadata_respects_page_size`: Page size honored\n\n### Search & Filter Tests\n- `test_search_by_keyword_returns_matches`: Keyword search finds matches\n- `test_search_by_keyword_no_matches`: Empty results when no matches\n- `test_filter_by_type`: Type filter returns correct subset\n- `test_filter_by_status`: Status filter working\n- `test_filter_by_tags`: Tag filtering returns matching metadata\n- `test_filter_combination`: Multiple filters combined with AND\n- `test_sort_by_created_asc`: Sort by created ascending\n- `test_sort_by_name_desc`: Sort by name descending\n\n### Import/Export Tests\n- `test_export_metadata_to_json`: JSON file created with correct content\n- `test_export_multiple_metadata`: Batch export working\n- `test_import_metadata_from_json`: Metadata created from JSON\n- `test_import_validates_data`: Invalid JSON raises ValidationError\n- `test_import_preserves_id`: ID preserved when specified\n- `test_import_generates_id_when_missing`: New ID assigned when not specified\n\n### Error Handling Tests\n- `test_validation_error_includes_field_path`: Error message has field path\n- `test_storage_error_wrapped`: Storage errors wrapped in MetadataError\n- `test_concurrent_update_handled`: Concurrent modification handled gracefully\n\n## Integration Tests\n\n### Happy Path\n- `test_full_metadata_lifecycle`: Create → Read → Update → Delete\n- `test_search_and_filter_workflow`: Create multiple, search, filter\n- `test_import_export_roundtrip`: Export then import preserves data\n\n### Error Scenarios\n- `test_duplicate_id_handling`: Duplicate ID handled appropriately\n- `test_corrupted_storage_recovery`: Graceful handling of storage errors\n- `test_concurrent_modification`: Last-write-wins or conflict detection\n\n## Test Data\n- Sample agent metadata fixtures\n- Invalid metadata for validation testing\n- Mock storage implementation\n- Test JSON files for import/export\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tests.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tests.md","time":{"start":1775896358362,"end":1775896358386}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896358388,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7baba486001JglMurU0iu63I3","messageID":"msg_d7ba9ce290011vj4ownMuaLevc","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:19","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/notes.md","content":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Notes\n\n## Status\nInitialized: 2026-04-11\n\n## Open Questions\n- Should metadata support attachments/binary data?\n- How to handle metadata schema migrations?\n- Should we implement a caching layer for frequently accessed metadata?\n- What is the maximum metadata size limit?\n- Should we support metadata encryption for sensitive fields?\n\n## References\n- See AR-024 for service implementation patterns\n- Related to agent configuration management\n- Check existing storage implementations for interface alignment\n\n## Change Log\n- 2026-04-11: Initial scaffold created\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/notes.md","time":{"start":1775896358365,"end":1775896358387}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896358390,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7babb614001tEPDUDxY8SvNGw","messageID":"msg_d7ba9ce290011vj4ownMuaLevc","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:20","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md","content":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Delta Spec\n\n## Overview\nThis document describes the delta specification for implementing the MetadataService\nand data models in the cmd/cli module.\n\n## Current State\n- No centralized metadata management service\n- Metadata scattered in various configuration files\n- No schema validation for agent metadata\n- Limited search/query capabilities\n- No versioning for metadata changes\n\n## Target State\nA unified MetadataService that:\n- Provides centralized metadata management\n- Enforces schema validation via Pydantic models\n- Supports versioning for audit and rollback\n- Enables search and filtering capabilities\n- Provides import/export functionality\n\n## Delta Analysis\n\n### New Components\n1. **MetadataService** (`cmd/cli/internal/metadata_service.py`)\n   - Main service class for metadata operations\n   - CRUD operations with validation\n   - Search and query methods\n\n2. **Data Models** (`cmd/cli/models/metadata.py`)\n   - Pydantic-based schema definitions\n   - AgentMetadata model\n   - MetadataVersion model\n\n3. **Storage Interface** (`cmd/cli/internal/storage_interface.py`)\n   - Abstract storage interface\n   - Pluggable backend support\n\n4. **Exceptions** (`cmd/cli/exceptions/metadata.py`)\n   - MetadataError base class\n   - ValidationError, NotFoundError, etc.\n\n### Modified Components\n- None (this is a new service layer)\n\n### Dependencies\n- pydantic library for data validation\n- Existing storage backends (file, database)\n\n## Interface Specification\n\n### MetadataService Class\n```python\nclass MetadataService:\n    def __init__(self, storage: MetadataStorage = None)\n    def create_metadata(self, data: dict) -> AgentMetadata\n    def get_metadata(self, metadata_id: str) -> AgentMetadata\n    def update_metadata(self, metadata_id: str, data: dict) -> AgentMetadata\n    def delete_metadata(self, metadata_id: str) -> None\n    def list_metadata(self, page: int = 1, page_size: int = 50) -> List[AgentMetadata]\n    def search_metadata(self, query: str, filters: dict = None) -> List[AgentMetadata]\n    def export_metadata(self, metadata_ids: List[str], filepath: str) -> None\n    def import_metadata(self, filepath: str) -> List[AgentMetadata]\n```\n\n## Implementation Notes\n- Use Pydantic v2 for validation\n- Support async operations where beneficial\n- Soft delete for data recovery\n- JSON format for import/export compatibility\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775896358368,"end":1775896358389}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896358755,"sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba9e440001aGyZp1dHbEm7em","messageID":"msg_d7ba9ce290011vj4ownMuaLevc","sessionID":"ses_28456ee41ffeBVl5njyNx1JzXZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-025\ntitle: MetadataService 与数据模型\nmodule: cmd/cli\nlanguage: Python\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型\n# Module: cmd/cli\n# Language: Python\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: service-layer\n  description: |\n    Implement a MetadataService class within the cmd/cli module to manage\n    agent metadata and data models. This service will provide a centralized\n    abstraction for CRUD operations on agent metadata, schema validation,\n    and metadata versioning to support agent discovery and configuration management.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - MetadataService class implementation\n    - Agent metadata CRUD operations (create, read, update, delete)\n    - Data model schema definition and validation\n    - Metadata versioning support\n    - Search and query capabilities for metadata\n    - Import/export functionality for metadata\n    - Integration with existing storage backend\n  out:\n    - UI for metadata management (separate AR)\n    - Distributed metadata synchronization\n    - Metadata caching layer (separate AR)\n    - Complex query language (SQL-like)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - MetadataService provides clean API for all metadata operations\n  - Schema validation ensures data integrity\n  - Versioning tracks metadata changes over time\n  - Search supports filtering by multiple criteria\n  - Import/export uses standard JSON format\n  - Error handling provides clear messages for validation failures\n  - Unit testable with mock storage backend\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - https://json-schema.org/\n  - https://docs.pydantic.dev/\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 3\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775896358344,"end":1775896358752}}}}
